   AUTHOR: Adrian Aichner <aichner@ecf.teradyne.com>
    WHERE: <rxsiuzebpgp.fsf@midnight.ecf.teradyne.com>

STATUS: Pending
 SINCE: 11-Oct-1997
 ADDED: 27-Sep-1997
REASON: Included John Heidemann <johnh@isi.edu>'s bbdb-snarf, since it 
        seemed to do a better job at finding things.  One of the above 
        (likely Adrian's) will be integrated.  What I'll likely do is
        have bbdb-snarf attack the sig.  Then we'll look at the from
        header and ask if the addresses are different.
